high_descs: Turn around and walk few steps towards the fridge.
Open the peppershaker and pick up the jar from the last peppershaker.
Turn left and walk few steps straight and turn right towards the cabinet.
Open the cabinet door and place the peppershaker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the PepperShaker on the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step towards the fridge that is nearby, on your left.
Take a peppershaker out of the fridge.
Move to a cabinet that is just to the left of the fridge.
Put the peppershaker inside the cabinet under the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the PepperShaker inside the Cabinet below the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and look at the fridge.
Open the peppershaker and take the lamp from the peppershaker and close the peppershaker.
Turn left and right and look in the cabinet.
Open the bottom of the cabinet and put the peppershaker inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: To get the PepperShaker from Cabinet to table rack.
